    "description": "<p>Flex builds great products for customers that create value and improve people’s lives. Building on our 50+ year history of manufacturing, the ~160,000-member Flex Family across 30 countries is at the heart of everything we do. Our values-driven and high-performing culture is rooted in doing the right thing always, collaboration, and resilient ingenuity. With employee safety, development, and inclusiveness as top priorities, we believe in creating the right work environment that empowers everyone to thrive. We bring the technology innovation, supply chain, and manufacturing expertise needed in a constantly evolving world and proudly touch nearly every industry and aspect of people’s lives for the better.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>As a Global 500 and 2021 Fortune World’s Most Admired Company</strong>, we’re growing the Flex Family. We’re looking for people to join the industry’s best makers, problem-solvers, innovators, craftspeople and leaders to help create the extraordinary.</p>",
